headline.main: CARNEGIE STARTED AS A BOBBIN BOY; Came to America When He Was 12 Years Old and Left Some $500,000,000. MADE FORTUNE IN STEEL Rose to be Dominant Figure in Industrial World and GreatBenefactor. Wealth Put at $500,000,000. Becomes a Telegraph Messenger. His First Investment. Meets Sleeping Car Inventor. Adopts Bessemer Steel Process. His Peace Propaganda. His Famous Utterance. Honors Conferred on Him.

abstract: death; career; port.; tributes; list of gifts
snippet: Until he was a septuagenarian, Andrew Carnegie believed that he was born in 1837. Then on a return visit to his native town in Scotland he learned that the date 1837 in the church records merely meant that the records were commenced in that year, ...
